PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1989-6/810 of May 4, 1989, which authorized the Department of National Defence to enter into an exchange of titles to various pieces of land situate at the Moose Jaw Armoury, in the City of MOOSE JAW, SASKATCHEWAN, so as to substitute a revised description of the lands thereby intended to be exchanged.
